85
00:05:47.180 --> 00:05:50.741
But if you spent it.
it would be like shopping.

86
00:05:52.785 --> 00:05:55.379
Say I bought a great pair of shoes.

87
00:05:55.588 --> 00:06:00.548
Know what I'd hear with every step?
"Not mine. Not mine. Not mine."

88
